"Your right. I'm being silly."
She smiled for him.  She was glad to be with him.  She was happy that he 
wasn't harmed in battle.

She kissed him tenderly on the cheek.
"One question, what did Megatrton mean by "enjoy" your fembot? I don't 
understand. Please explain this to me?  I don't want to anger him in the 
future by misunderstanding him."
She smiled with her innicence showing through.
